<p style="font-family:Roboto, Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">Please see below for the updates and information posted to date by NBASD:</p>
<p style="font-family:Roboto, Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">April 15, 2020 - <a href="https://www.nbasd.org/sys/content/newspost/f27709802e1240c0926c00762489e778" target="_blank">School Closure - Education Updates &amp; Additional Information</a></p>
